show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/5X45k2
show.description: Mera Handsome Bodyguard is a high-stakes romantic thriller that follows Aarohi Mehta, a sharp and confident CEO, whose life takes a dramatic turn when she hires Kabir Rana, a mysterious hotel security guard, as her personal bodyguard. What begins as a fake marriage for reputation soon blossoms into real love, but secrets from Kabir’s hidden past resurface—revealing him as an ex-army intelligence officer with enemies still at large. Together, they battle corporate sabotage, personal betrayals, and a deadly conspiracy led by Raghav Thakur, a corrupt former officer and Kabir’s nemesis. At the heart of it all is Gudiya, Kabir’s daughter—and the key to a national scandal. With love, loyalty, and truth on the line, will this trio survive the storm?
